                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>During a conversation on September 12, 1947, the Secretary of State and French
                    Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_BH1">Bonnet</persName> discussed the question
                    of the future regime for the Ruhr; see <persName corresp="#p_HJD1">John
                        Hickerson</persName>’s memorandum of the conversation, in the documentation
                    on concern of the United States with political and economic developments
                    relating to France, in <ref target="frus1947v03">volume <hi rend="smallcaps"
                            >iii</hi>
                    </ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
